      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING SIGRID (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Mt Gambier in a handy 29.57 beating Belair Betty. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Looks the one to beat. PAW BENNETT (5) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten half a length into second (23.53) at Horsham in a Grade 5 over 410m. Hard to beat again. REV IAN (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing seventh (30.72) at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to bounce back to best. PAW LYNETTE (2) warrants respect although new to this track.",
